import { useHistory } from "react-router";

export default function Authenticated( props ) {

    const history = useHistory();

    const RenderSwitch = () => {
        switch ( props.path ) {
            case ( "/" ):
                props.loggedIn ?
                    history.push( "/frontpage" ) :
                    history.push( "/" )
                break

            case ( "/access" ):
                props.loggedIn ?
                    history.push( "/frontpage" ) :
                    history.push( "/access" )
                break

            case ( "/frontpage" ):
                props.loggedIn ?
                    history.push( "/frontpage" ) :
                    history.push( "/access" )
                break

            default:
                history.push( "/access" )
        }
    }

    RenderSwitch()

    return null
}
